==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Unmonopolize
<hw>Un`mo*nop"o*lize</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[1st pref.
<ets>un-</ets> + <ets>monopolize</ets>.]</ety> <def>To recover or
release from the state of being monopolized.</def> <mark>[R.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q><qex>Unmonopolizing</qex> the rewards of learning and
industry.</q> <rj><qau>Milton.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Unmoor</ent>⟦br⟧
